Package: bigR
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Handling of Large Datasets in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jomana", "Abdelrahman",
      email = "jomanaabdelrahman28@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a seamless way to work with large datasets in R 
    by automatically selecting the best backend for performance. It supports
    out-of-core processing, parallel computation, and optimized data 
    manipulation functions while maintaining a syntax familiar to R practitioners.
